      • getCarbRatio

        public long getCarbRatio()
        Returns:
        the ratio from 1 milliunit : __ grams, or 1 unit : (__ * 1000) grams. If the carb ratio in the pump is 1u : 6 grams, then the long value returned is 6000

      • getMaxBolusAmount

        public int getMaxBolusAmount()

      • getMaxBolusHourlyTotal

        public long getMaxBolusHourlyTotal()

      • getMaxBolusEventsExceeded

      • getMaxIobEventsExceeded

        public boolean getMaxIobEventsExceeded()

      • getIsAutopopAllowed

        public boolean getIsAutopopAllowed()
